'''幼發拉底之盾行動'''是[[土耳其|土耳其]]出兵[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]的軍事行動，於2016年8月24日開始，至2017年3月29日由土耳其方面宣佈成功完成。<ref name=completed/>第一個攻勢是[[自由叙利亚军|自由叙利亚军]]在土耳其軍隊支援下，向[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]佔據的敘利亞[[阿勒頗省|阿勒頗省]]城鎮[[賈拉布魯斯|賈拉布魯斯]]及附近地區發動進攻，阻止敘利亞庫爾德族武裝於[[曼比季攻勢|曼比季攻勢]]獲勝後在[[幼發拉底河|幼發拉底河]]以西地區佔領更多土地。

「幼發拉底之盾行動」是土耳其對本次軍事行動的代號。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-08/27/c_129257712.htm |title=土耳其出兵叙利亚 目标不只是反恐 |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-08-27 |accessdate=2016-08-28 |archive-date=2016-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827001928/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-08/27/c_129257712.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>土耳其總統[[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|埃爾多安]]在2016年8月24日表明本次行動既針對伊斯蘭國也針對[[人民保衛軍|敘利亞庫爾德人]]「恐怖團體」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20160824-erdogan-says-syria-operation-aimed-jihadists-kurdish-pyd|title=Erdogan says Syria operation aimed at IS jihadists, Kurdish PYD|date=24 August 2016|publisher=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825183523/http://www.france24.com/en/20160824-erdogan-says-syria-operation-aimed-jihadists-kurdish-pyd|archivedate=2016年8月25日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/turkish-army-backed-rebels-advance-inside-syria-on-isil.aspx?pageID=238&nID=103174&NewsCatID=352|title=Turkish army-backed rebels advance inside Syria on ISIL - MIDEAST|publisher=|accessdate=2016-08-25|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019074013/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/turkish-army-backed-rebels-advance-inside-syria-on-isil.aspx?pageID=238&nID=103174&NewsCatID=352|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==賈拉布魯斯攻勢==
8月24日早上，土耳其軍隊猛烈炮轟[[賈拉布魯斯|賈拉布魯斯]]的伊斯蘭國據點，並出動空軍空襲11個目標。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.trend.az/world/turkey/2652129.html|title=Turkish jets bomb Daesh targets in Jarabulus|work=Trend News Agency|date=24 August 2016|access-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101125014/http://en.trend.az/world/turkey/2652129.html|archive-date=2016-11-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同日稍後，土耳其特種部隊和多輛相信載有親土耳其[[敘利亞反對派|敘利亞反對派]]武裝分子的卡車跟隨土軍坦克越過邊境進入敘利亞。<ref name="bbc.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-37171995|title=Turkey sends tanks into northern Syria|work=bbc|date=24 August 2016|accessdate=2016-08-25|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118120049/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-37171995|dead-url=no}}</ref>有數以百計的自由敘利亞軍戰士加入進攻賈拉布魯斯。<ref name=f24/>

土軍與反對派武裝於8月24日攻佔賈拉布魯斯，過程中僅遇到少許抵抗。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.businessinsider.com/syrian-rebels-isis-jarablus-2016-8?r=US&IR=T|title=Turkish and US-backed Syrian rebels have captured a key ISIS border crossing|work=Business Insider|date=24 August 2016|accessdate=2016-08-25|archive-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826110432/http://uk.businessinsider.com/syrian-rebels-isis-jarablus-2016-8?r=US&IR=T|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="edition.cnn.com">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/08/24/middleeast/turkish-troops-isis-syria-operation/|title=Turkey sends tanks into Syria to battle ISIS|work=CNN|date=24 August 2016|accessdate=2016-08-25|archive-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825175739/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/08/24/middleeast/turkish-troops-isis-syria-operation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>據報一大群伊斯蘭國戰士已撤退至[[巴卜|巴卜]]。<ref name="Al-Jazeera">{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/08/syria-turkish-backed-rebels-seize-jarablus-isil-160824162712114.html|title=Syria: Turkish-backed rebels 'seize' Jarablus from ISIL|work=Al Jazeera|date=25 August 2016|accessdate=2016-08-25|archive-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825183359/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/08/syria-turkish-backed-rebels-seize-jarablus-isil-160824162712114.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===與庫族部隊的衝突===
到訪土耳其的美國副總統[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]於8月24日要求庫爾德族[[人民保衛軍|人民保衛軍]]撤離[[曼比季|曼比季]]，返回[[幼發拉底河|幼發拉底河]]以東地區，<ref name="bbc.com"/>被人民保衛軍即日拒絕<ref>{{cite web|url=https://anfenglish.com/kurdistan/ypg-we-will-not-retreat-from-west-of-euphrates|title=YPG: We will not retreat from west of Euphrates|work=ANF News|date=24 August 2016|accessdate=24 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827102323/http://www.anfenglish.com/kurdistan/ypg-we-will-not-retreat-from-west-of-euphrates|dead-url=no}}</ref>。親[[敘利亞民主力量|敘利亞民主力量]]的「賈拉布魯斯軍事委員會」宣佈他們不會把賈拉布魯斯拱手讓予土耳其支持的反對派團體，並指那些團體「與伊斯蘭國無異」。自由敘利亞軍嘗試進入位於賈拉布魯斯以南，被敘民主力量控制的Amarinah村，遭到敘民主力量抵抗，最終自由軍被擊退。<ref name=fight>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/turkish-backed-rebels-fight-us-backed-rebels-aleppo/|title=Turkish-backed rebels fight US-backed rebels in Aleppo|author=Izat Charkatli|work=al-Masdar News|date=24 August 2016|accessdate=24 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825194846/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/turkish-backed-rebels-fight-us-backed-rebels-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://aranews.net/2016/08/clashes-break-turkish-backed-rebels-syrian-democratic-forces/|title=Clashes break out between Turkish-backed rebels and Syrian Democratic Forces|work=ARA News|date=25 August 2016|accessdate=25 August 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826191541/http://aranews.net/2016/08/clashes-break-turkish-backed-rebels-syrian-democratic-forces/|archivedate=2016年8月26日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=49839|title=The countryside of Jarablos witnesses the first clash between the fighters of the faction that controlled Jarablos city against Syria Democratic Forces|work=SOHR|date=24 August 2016|accessdate=2016-08-25|archive-date=2016-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007194511/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=49839|dead-url=no}}</ref>

面對土耳其增派軍隊進入敘利亞北部並威脅攻撃庫族部隊，先前拒絕撤走的人民保衛軍於8月25日宣佈參與攻佔曼比季的部隊在完成任務後已撤返基地，並把曼比季的據點和軍事指揮權交予當地人組成的「曼比季軍事委員會」接管。[[堅定決心行動|堅定決心行動]]發言人表示敘民主力量的部隊大多已返回幼發拉底河以東，只有少量部隊留下協助掃蕩殘留敵軍和清除遺留的[[簡易爆炸裝置|簡易爆炸裝置]]（IED）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKCN110124|title=Syrian Kurdish YPG says it returned to base after Manbij's capture|work=Reuters|date=25 August 2016|accessdate=25 August 2016|archive-date=2022-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220328042116/https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKCN110124}}</ref>

8月27日早上，人民保衛軍在賈拉布魯斯以南遭到土耳其戰機空襲。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-08/27/c_135638516.htm |title=Turkish warplanes strike YPG militants in northern Syria |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-08-27 |accessdate=2016-08-28 |archive-date=2016-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828132513/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-08/27/c_135638516.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>同日人民保衛軍在賈拉布魯斯附近攻擊土軍坦克，1名土國士兵陣亡。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-08/28/c_135638837.htm |title=Update: Turkish solider killed by Kurdish rocket attack in northern Syria |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-08-28 |accessdate=2016-08-28 |archive-date=2016-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828131831/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-08/28/c_135638837.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月28日，土耳其宣稱當日有25名庫族武裝分子死於土軍空襲。<ref name=bbc20160828>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-37208941 |title=Syria war: Turkey kills 25 people in latest round of air strikes |work=BBC News |date=2016-08-28 |accessdate=2016-08-28 |archive-date=2016-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828121342/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-37208941 |dead-url=no }}</ref>同日據報有至少40名平民死於土軍炮轟和空襲。<ref name=40dead>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3762099/Turkish-bombardment-kills-20-civilians-Syria-monitor.html |title=Turkey ramps up Syria offensive with deadly bombings |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2016-08-28 |accessdate=2016-08-28 |archive-date=2016-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160829124633/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3762099/Turkish-bombardment-kills-20-civilians-Syria-monitor.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

到8月29日，土耳其支持的武裝分子已佔領多條原由[[人民保衛軍|人民保衛軍]]控制的村莊，並進軍至[[薩朱爾河|薩朱爾河]]北岸。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/free-syrian-army-engage-isis-ypg-morning-jarablus/|title=Free Syrian Army engage with ISIS and YPG this morning in Jarablus|work=al-Masdar News|author=Paul Antonopoulos|date=2016-08-29|accessdate=2016-08-31|archive-date=2016-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830162337/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/free-syrian-army-engage-isis-ypg-morning-jarablus/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==肅清伊斯蘭國在土敘邊境餘下據點==
9月3日，土耳其增派更多坦克到敘利亞的拉伊（al-Rai）鎮協助反對派向東推進，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-turkey-idUSKCN1190GT |title=Turkish tanks roll into Syria, opening new line of attack |last= |first= |date=2016-09-04 |website= |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2016-09-06 |archive-date=2016-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160906203411/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-turkey-idUSKCN1190GT |dead-url=no }}</ref>以實現東西兩路會師。

9月4日，土耳其方面宣佈親土耳其的反對派已佔領土敘邊境上最後一個原由伊斯蘭國控制的村莊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/4478871/isis-territory-turkey-syria-border/?xid=homepage|title=Turkey Says ISIS Has Lost All Territory Along the Turkey-Syria Border|last1=Mroue|first1=Bassem|first2=Zeynep|last2=Bilginsoy|date=2016-09-04|website=time.com|publisher=Time|accessdate=2016-09-05|archive-date=2016-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160905031751/http://time.com/4478871/isis-territory-turkey-syria-border/?xid=homepage|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/09/syria-war-isil-driven-turkey-syria-border-160904164425932.html|title=Syria's war: ISIL 'driven out' from Turkey-Syria border|date=4 September 2016|publisher=Al Jazeera|accessdate=5 September 2016|archive-date=2016-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160906154852/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/09/syria-war-isil-driven-turkey-syria-border-160904164425932.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==後續攻勢==
2016年9月28日，[[達比克攻勢|達比克攻勢]]開始。10月15日，親土耳其的反對派部隊已接近完全包圍[[達比克|達比克]]。<ref name="imminent">{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/battle-dabiq-imminent-rebel-forces-advance-isis-aleppo/ |title=Battle of Dabiq imminent as rebel forces advance against ISIS in Aleppo |accessdate=2016-10-16 |archive-date=2017-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014065804/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/battle-dabiq-imminent-rebel-forces-advance-isis-aleppo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>次日反對派部隊宣稱在伊斯蘭國撤出達比克後已佔領該地。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-37670998|title=Syria conflict: Rebels 'capture' IS stronghold of Dabiq|date=2016-10-16|work=BBC News|access-date=2016-10-16|archive-date=2019-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423231306/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-37670998|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==巴卜之戰==
2016年11月6日，土耳其與敘反對派的聯軍發起[[巴卜之戰|巴卜之戰]]，經過逾3個月的戰鬥後，土耳其領導的聯軍於2017年2月23日從伊斯蘭國手上攻佔[[阿勒颇省|阿勒颇省]]城市[[巴卜|巴卜]]。

==攻勢受阻==
2017年1月中，敘利亞政府軍向[[阿勒頗省|阿勒頗省]]東部的伊斯蘭國控制區發動[[東阿勒頗攻勢_(2017年)|攻勢]]，意圖阻斷土耳其與敘反對派聯軍的南下路徑。敘政府軍收復大量村鎮，並於2017年2月27日到達[[曼比季|曼比季]]的[[敘利亞民主力量|敘利亞民主力量]]控制區，使土耳其軍無法以打擊伊斯蘭國的名義繼續向南推進。

2017年3月初，[[土耳其|土耳其]]方面警告庫爾德族武裝離開[[曼比季|曼比季]]，否則將會進攻他們。美國迅速介入，派遣少量美軍進駐曼比季，阻止土耳其向曼比季採取軍事行動。<ref name=xh20170308>{{cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-03/08/c_129503462.htm |title=美国增兵曼比季 叙北部重镇上演“四国演义” |publisher=新華網 |date=2017-03-08 |accessdate=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2017-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308005906/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-03/08/c_129503462.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=reuters20170306>{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-usa-idUSKBN16D29G?il=0 |title=U.S. military deploys forces in Syria's Manbij in new effort |publisher=Reuters |date=2017-03-06 |accessdate=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2017-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313180004/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-usa-idUSKBN16D29G?il=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

